//
// Two sibling cyclostatic loops on the same fifo (#2463): each loop's
// trailing release drains its hoisted carry before the next loop runs. The
// IRON design in test.py declares both loops; the peel rewrite keeps the
// producer-side lock draining instead of deadlocking.
//
// REQUIRES: ryzen_ai_npu2, peano, xrt_python_bindings
//
// RUN: %run_on_npu2% %python %S/test.py
